<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10683</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西看到化学烟雾穿过更多的农场土地。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>沉重的脚步声震动着大地。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不知道蓝狒狒是不是就在那团烟雾里。”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，它正往美罗城的方向走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31600</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我得阻止它！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31600</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36106</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西快速地飞向那团化学烟雾。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36106</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它现在正在曼先生的玉米地里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她深吸了一口气，然后吐出。呼！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50844</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一只巨大的手从烟雾中伸出来，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50751</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53764</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>打了罗西一下。砰！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53765</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55854</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她在空中翻滚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55854</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58434</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当罗西落地的时候，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58434</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60617</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那团烟雾不见了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60618</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63991</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一只巨大的狒狒站在地里，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63992</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67654</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>身上都是亮晶晶的化学物质。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67654</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69653</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狒狒在挠痒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它看上去很生气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“天啊！”罗西说。“那肯定是蓝狒狒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79780</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不过它有大楼那么高！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79781</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83069</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>肯定是化学物质让它长高的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83069</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87573</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇呜！哇呜！”蓝狒狒吼叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87573</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大狒狒挠了挠它的身子，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后走向罗西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95182</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狒狒的嘴张得大大的，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95183</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>露出又大又尖的牙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98854</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101369</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“天啊！”罗西叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101370</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104686</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>蓝狒狒狠狠打向罗西，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104687</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西快速躲开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110636</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狒狒再一次吼叫起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110636</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115640</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他挠着痒，一脚踩向曼先生的仓库。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115640</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119885</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哗啦！仓库变得粉碎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119884</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>曼先生从屋里跑了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126267</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“出什么事了，我的……？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126266</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129570</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他抬头看到蓝狒狒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129571</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136268</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”曼先生跑进屋子，躲在床下面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136284</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141956</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇呜！哇呜！”蓝狒狒生气地吼叫着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141956</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147037</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它跺着脚，挠着痒。“哇呜！哇呜！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147043</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151153</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西看到蓝狒狒在挠肩膀。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151153</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155320</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，它转过身，跺着脚，穿过地里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155320</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158871</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它正往美罗城方向走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158871</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163118</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不能让蓝狒狒到美罗城去！”罗西想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163128</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166567</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它会毁了美罗城所有的大楼的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西飞向大狒狒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173076</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她双手抱住狒狒的脚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173076</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的身上沾满了亮晶晶的化学物质。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇呜！”蓝狒狒猛地抬起脚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186071</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它挣脱了罗西，又使劲儿踢了她一脚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186070</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188845</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西从空中掉了下来，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188846</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192251</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>撞在一辆拖拉机上。“哎呦！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194251</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西站起来，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198003</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>满身都是亮晶晶的化学物质。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198003</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199740</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她挠了一下痒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199740</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接着又挠了几下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206688</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呃！”罗西的脸变红了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206699</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209007</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我为什么这么痒呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209007</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她跺着脚，不停地挠。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西咬着牙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220505</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！太可怕了！我痒死了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220504</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我变得越来越生气了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>